name: Janet Ouusu
description:
I am a strong woman when it is needed and a little weak girl when I am next to a strong man. I love to laugh and I think I am a very cheerful person. People always say they can rely on me and that is why I have a lot of friends. I love to just dream and imagine my future life. I simply enjoy everything and this way I feel happy.
Of course, I can write here a lot of information describing perfect me. But I am not going to do that. I want to say, that I am a woman. And there is nothing to add. I know, that I am able to give everything to my future beloved man for making him happy and satisfied beside me. My heart seems to have no borders for love and gentle for my lovely man. Love is all that I want to give to that special man. So I want to begin to create new world with you. I dream to be with a real strong man who knows how to be happy. I need just a little of his love.E-mail me on JANNETOUUSU at GM . com
